'''vagus nerve''' 

# {{anatomy}} Either of the tenth pair of [[cranial nerve]]s, which extends from the [[brainstem]] down into the [[abdomen]]. Branches of these important nerves supply the [[tongue]], [[larynx]], [[lung]]s, [[gut]], and [[heart]].

